             was indicted for <rs id="t17900224-38-off219" type="offenceDescription">
                     <interp inst="t17900224-38-off219" type="offenceCategory" value="theft"></interp>
                     <interp inst="t17900224-38-off219" type="offenceSubcategory" value="grandLarceny"></interp>
               feloniously stealing, on the <rs id="t17900224-38-cd220" type="crimeDate">13th<xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="179002240043"></xptr>of February</rs>
                     <join result="offenceCrimeDate" targOrder="Y" targets="t17900224-38-off219 t17900224-38-cd220"></join>, in the parish of St. Andrew by the Wardrobe, two bushels and a half of coals, value 2 s.
            </rs> the property of 
               <persName id="t17900224-38-victim397" type="victimName">
                     <rs id="t17900224-38-viclabel221" type="occupation">
                     
                        <persName id="t17900224-38-person398">
